features: CLEARER SKIN, ZERO PAIN – Say’ goodbye’ to painful adhesive nose strips, and eliminate excess oil and extract impurities with our pain-free absorption alternative.
VISIBLE RESULTS IN 6 HOURS – Our fast-acting nose pore strips will help you achieve tighter pores and a healthy nose within hours.
PERFECT FOR OILY PORES – Specifically tailored for those suffering from oily pores, as it gently removes excess oil and impurities to improve the appearance of your nose.
SHRINK PORES & BLACKHEAD REMOVER STRIPS – Reduce the size of your pores and prevent blackheads with our award-winning hydrocolloid nose pore strips.
DERMATOLOGICALLY TESTED – Clinically tested and dermatologically approved for all skin types, these gentle and non-drying patches won't irritate your nose.
VEGAN FRIENDLY & CRUELTY-FREE KOREAN SKINCARE – We're committed to the planet - offering vegan products, no animal testing, and biodegradable, eco-conscious ingredients.
